INSTALLATION:
sudo layman -S && sudo layman -a rainyday

contains:

x11-misc/bumblebee
    gentoo support of solution for using your nv gfx-adapter on optimus laptops

x11-wm/coldsufion
    my own try to make cousy usable and great looking environment with compiz as wm

app-misc/libspnav
    free, compatible alternative to the proprietary 3Dconnexion device driver and SDK,
    for their 3D input devices (called "space navigator", "space pilot", "space traveller", etc).
    homepage: http://spacenav.sourceforge.net

gnome-base/gnome-as-i-want
    a slightly modified ebuild for gnome-meta package, with exception of couple details.
